Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper deals with autonomous driving and trajectory prediction in urban scenarios. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes a probabilistic prediction framework based on a dynamic Bayesian network. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the paper involves tracking agents in a scene. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes context-dependent motion models to define the behavior of drivers. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is relevant as the paper deals with controlling autonomous vehicles in complex, urban scenarios.
